title: BRIEF-Raute Oyj ‍To Distribute Dividend Of EUR 1.25 Per A Series A And K Share
text: March 22, 2018 / 6:18 PM / Updated 27 minutes ago BRIEF-Raute Oyj ‍To Distribute Dividend Of EUR 1.25 Per A Series A And K Share Reuters Staff 1 Min Read March 22 (Reuters) - Raute Oyj: * ‍TO DISTRIBUTE A DIVIDEND OF EUR 1.25 PER A SERIES A AND K SHARE, WITH PAYMENT DATE 4 APRIL 2018​ * SAYS ‍ANNUAL GENERAL MEETING ELECTED BOARD OF DIRECTORS FOR NEXT TERM OF OFFICE ENDING AT ANNUAL GENERAL MEETING IN 2019​ * SAYS ‍ERKKI PEHU-LEHTONEN WAS ELECTED CHAIRMAN OF BOARD OF DIRECTORS​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
